'''AI Learning Roadmap

Stage 1 – Foundations
Goal: Build strong math & programming skills.

1. Mathematics for AI
Linear Algebra → vectors, matrices, matrix multiplication
Probability & Statistics → mean, variance, Bayes theorem
Calculus → derivatives, gradient descent

2. Python Programming
Syntax, loops, functions
NumPy, Pandas for data handling
Matplotlib, Seaborn for visualization

3. Data Skills
Data cleaning & preprocessing
Handling missing data, encoding categorical variables
Normalization & standardization

Stage 2 – Core Machine Learning
Goal: Understand how machines learn from data.

1. ML Basics
Supervised Learning: Linear Regression, Logistic Regression, Decision Trees
Unsupervised Learning: K-Means, PCA, Hierarchical Clustering
Model evaluation: Accuracy, Precision, Recall, F1-score, ROC-AUC

2. Advanced ML
Random Forest, Gradient Boosting (XGBoost, LightGBM, CatBoost)
Support Vector Machines
KNN, Naive Bayes

Stage 3 – Deep Learning
Goal: Master neural networks & deep architectures.
1. Neural Network Basics
Perceptron, Multilayer Perceptron
Backpropagation, activation functions

2. Specialized Architectures
CNN (Convolutional Neural Networks) – images
RNN & LSTM (Long Short-Term Memory) – sequences
Transformers – advanced NLP models

3. Frameworks
TensorFlow, PyTorch, Keras

Stage 4 – Specializations
Goal: Pick an AI domain to focus on.

1. Natural Language Processing (NLP)
Tokenization, stemming, lemmatization
Word embeddings (Word2Vec, GloVe)
Transformers (BERT, GPT)

2. Computer Vision
Image classification, object detection (YOLO, Faster R-CNN)
OpenCV basics
Transfer Learning

3. Reinforcement Learning
Agents, environment, reward system
Q-Learning, Deep Q-Networks
Policy gradient methods

Stage 5 – AI in Practice
Goal: Deploy and manage AI models.

1. Model Deployment
Flask, FastAPI, Streamlit
Docker for containerization

2. MLOps
Git/GitHub for version control
CI/CD pipelines
Cloud platforms (AWS, GCP, Azure)

3.Ethics & Responsible AI
Bias, fairness, privacy

Stage 6 – Projects & Portfolio
Goal: Build real-world experience.

Customer churn prediction (ML)
Image classification app (CNN)
Sentiment analysis chatbot (NLP)
Game-playing AI (Reinforcement Learning)
AI model deployed on a web app'''
